Description:
Young families will delight!
Young families will delight in this character filled - solid brick family home. It offers a practical single level floor plan, idyllic rear garden with a swimming pool and a level of convenience that is hard to beat. Tucked away in a court, this home is private, secure and a place you will be glad to call home.
Featuring floor boards and exposed brick walls, the floor plan begins with an inviting lounge room/dining that extends to the original kitchen/meals complete with gas cooking appliances. There are also 3 good-sized bedrooms, updated family bathroom and practical laundry. A large backyard with a swimming pool creates a wonderful place for family and friends to enjoy. Additional features include roller shutters, double carport with ample off street parking and garden shed.
With easy access to bus, schools, train station, shops and parks - now is the time to act.

Description:
Estimated Completion Date APRIL - JUNE 2020
St.A is a premium development, unlike anything else in St Albans and surrounding suburbs.
St.A offers freehold title, architecturally designed homes within a master planned estate, only 16km from the CBD.
A landscaped central park is proposed at St.A, which will include a children's playground, barbeque shelter and open grassed areas for residents and the local community to enjoy.
St.A is a project by award winning developer Cedar Woods, which has a long history of creating vibrant residential Communities around Australia.
Hudson Release
A short stroll away, you will find two supermarkets, green grocers, chemists, newsagents, restaurants and cafes and personal and professional services.
Architecturally three bedroom home.
St.A combines innovative design with contemporary architecture to create spacious and light filled homes
Environmentally friendly home, including a 6-star energy rating and rainwater tanks
The St.A site is 350m south of the new St Albans Train Station and 1.4km north of the new Ginifer Train Station on the Sunbury line, which provides direct access to the CBD and wider north-west region of Melbourne.
Only 16kms from Melbourne's CBD
NBN Ready!

Description:
Timeless Design, Outstanding Lifestyle
Purchase this beautiful property in the ever popular suburb of Keilor Downs and you will come home everyday to picturesque surroundings and a safe, welcoming neighbourhood. Offering a spacious and flexible internal layout, modern interior decor and sitting proudly on a nicely landscaped 650m2 block of land, 31 Copernicus Way will have you feeling at home from the moment you enter the front door.
Within walking distance and in the zone of multiple schools including Keilor Downs College and Keilor Views Primary School. Keilor Central Shopping Centre, Watergardens Town Centre as well as Keilor Plains and Watergardens train stations are within easy reach as are major road networks including the Western Ring Road and Calder Freeway.
Features include;
* 4 large fitted bedrooms including 2 master bedrooms with en suite and walk-in wardrobes (one upstairs and one downstairs)
* Spacious lounge room with cathedral ceilings
* Updated kitchen with stone benches and ample storage space
* Open plan meals and living area with polished concrete flooring and cathedral ceilings
* Upstairs multi-purpose retreat
* Updated central bathroom
* Updated flooring throughout
* Internal access to the extra-large automatic double garage
* Drive through access to an additional carport
* Substantial land size of approximately 650m2
* Outdoor entertaining area overlooking the landscaped gardens
Also includes ducted heating, 2 split system air conditioners, ceiling fans, roller shutters, dishwasher and many other quality fixtures and fittings.
The perfect mix of classic charm and modern practicality!

Description:
Contemporary class, lifestyle ease
Clean lines and quality appointments make this near-new three bedroom two bathroom residence a standout for astute buyers keen on low maintenance living. Big on space, open plan living featuring solid hardwood floors and a designer two-tone CaesarStone island kitchen complete with full suite of stainless steel appliances opens to manicured low maintenance gardens showcasing built-in seating, quaint vertical garden and alfresco area for your entertaining pleasure. Excellence continues through carpeted bedrooms, designer bathrooms with oversized showers and stone topped vanities, master with ensuite and WIR, spacious laundry, powder room, plantation shutters, heating/cooling and garage with remote plus OSP. Enviably positioned a short walk to Centreway shops, cafes and Milleara Road buses, with easy access to the Calder and associated freeways and range of schools including Penleigh & Essendon Grammar, Keilor Heights Primary and Essendon Keilor College, inspection will impress.
